<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: defoliator -->
  <Defoliator.label>蝕葉器</Defoliator.label>
  <!-- EN: An area-denial device which annihilates nearby plants without affecting animals.\n\nIn planetary wars, these weapons are scattered across farmlands or jungles to deny the enemy food or cover. They're usually associated with orbital-drop mechanoid swarms. -->
  <Defoliator.description>一種能在不影響周圍動物情況下殺死附近植物的區域封鎖設備。\n\n在星際戰爭中，用以在不損壞領地的情況下除掉敵人的糧食供應和避難所。它們通常與軌道空投的機械體敵人相關。</Defoliator.description>
  
  <!-- EN: gloomlight -->
  <Gloomlight.label>幽光</Gloomlight.label>
  <!-- EN: A self-powered mechanoid light. Gloomlights can be deconstructed to yield valuable resources, or used as lights - but only if they are captured intact. The internal micro power cell will flame out and ruin the materials if the unit takes too much damage. -->
  <Gloomlight.description>自主供電的機械燈。幽光可以被拆卸以獲取有用的資源，或者直接用來照明——前提是它被完整捕獲。如果幽光受到太大的損傷，內部的微功率電池會超載燒毀。</Gloomlight.description>

  <!-- EN: unstable power cell -->
  <UnstablePowerCell.label>不穩定能量電池</UnstablePowerCell.label>
  <!-- EN: A mechanoid power generation unit. The vanometric power core will run forever, extracting energy from quantum foam fluctuations.\n\nAn internal amplifier system makes it unstable. If damaged, the unit will generate a massive explosion.\n\nSome brave humans steal these from mechanoids for their own use as power plants or defensive bombs. However, an unintentional detonation can be devastating. -->
  <UnstablePowerCell.description>一種機械族能源模塊。虛空核心將永遠運行，從量子波動中提取能量。\n\n內部放大器系統使其不穩定。如果受到損壞，這個裝置將產生巨大的爆炸。\n\n一些勇敢的人類從機械設備中偷來這些東西，自己用作發電廠或防禦炸彈。然而，無意的爆炸可能是毀滅性的。</UnstablePowerCell.description>
  
</LanguageData>